# keyd virtual keyboard — receives events from all physical keyboards via keyd.
# Uses us(altgr-intl) to restore Mod5 (AltGr/Right Alt) needed for dictation shortcut.
# No caps:escape here since keyd handles CapsLock at the evdev level.
